Class OraclePropertyGraphDataLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.pg.rdbms.OraclePropertyGraphDataLoader

  • public class OraclePropertyGraphDataLoader
extends Object
    This class implements the logic to load a property graph (in Oracle-defined flat files format) into supported backend database.
